1) DMZ0) /etc/bind/rtfm.com.br

	@	IN	NS	ns1.rtfm.com.br.
	@	IN	NS	ns2.rtfm.com.br. (DNS escravo)
	@	IN	MX	0 mail.rtfm.com.br. (email)
	ns1	IN	A	192.168.2.1	
	ns2	IN	A	192.168.2.2 (DNS escravo)
	mail	IN	A	192.168.2.2 (email)
	smtp	IN	CNAME	mail.rtfm.com.br. (email)
	imap	IN	CNAME	mail.rtfm.com.br. (email)
	webmail	IN	CNAME	www.rtfm.com.br.

2) DMZ1) (reiniciar o DNS)

